WEBVTT

02:01.960 --> 02:03.680
Miss, are you okay?

02:04.040 --> 02:06.200
Will that guy make a big deal out of this?

02:06.200 --> 02:08.060
Why isn't he answering the phone?

02:10.440 --> 02:11.720
Here, drink some water.

02:11.720 --> 02:12.880
Don't die of thirst here.

02:12.880 --> 02:14.340
We don't want any trouble.

02:14.880 --> 02:15.880
I'm begging you.

02:16.760 --> 02:17.690
Please let me go.

02:18.120 --> 02:19.380
I don't have any money.

02:19.640 --> 02:21.900
My grandmother is still in the hospital.

02:22.000 --> 02:23.400
I need to take care of her.

02:23.600 --> 02:25.560
We are not extorting you.

02:26.280 --> 02:27.040
Tell me,

02:27.400 --> 02:29.200
will Mu Qingyun come to save you?

02:30.079 --> 02:31.540
Mu Qingyun is still young.

02:31.680 --> 02:32.810
He's just immature.

02:33.960 --> 02:34.800
Let me go.

02:35.079 --> 02:36.120
When I get back,

02:36.920 --> 02:38.040
I'll find a time

02:38.280 --> 02:40.340
for him to apologize to you in person.

02:40.440 --> 02:41.040
Okay?

02:41.240 --> 02:42.520
No need to make an appointment.

02:42.520 --> 02:43.850
He's already on his way.

02:45.280 --> 02:46.680
What on earth do you want?

02:46.680 --> 02:48.200
What are you doing?

02:48.200 --> 02:50.240
Actually, I haven't quite decided.

02:50.760 --> 02:52.890
Just looking for a way to vent my anger.

02:54.440 --> 02:55.680
I'm begging you.

02:56.320 --> 02:57.880
Please don't hurt Mutou.

02:58.480 --> 02:59.960
Don't hurt Mutou.

03:00.000 --> 03:02.040
You're quite a loyal little girl.

03:04.280 --> 03:05.440
What do you want?

03:05.760 --> 03:08.120
What good does hurting him do for you?

03:08.480 --> 03:09.920
Watching him suffer

03:10.640 --> 03:11.600
makes me happy.

03:12.080 --> 03:13.210
That's the benefit.

03:13.520 --> 03:14.360
Bring her up.

03:15.800 --> 03:16.880
What are you doing?

03:17.960 --> 03:18.840
Let me go!

03:22.720 --> 03:25.040
Mutou, please don't come!

03:45.720 --> 03:47.040
What a big scene.

03:48.160 --> 03:49.960
Yuanbao, are you okay?

03:50.120 --> 03:52.880
Mutou, I'm fine. Just go!

03:53.480 --> 03:55.480
Why are you all just standing there?

03:55.800 --> 03:56.930
Are you a girl group?

03:58.560 --> 04:00.440
Cut the crap. Spit it out.

04:01.160 --> 04:01.920
Attack!

04:07.560 --> 04:08.520
Mutou!

04:12.920 --> 04:13.960
Mutou!

04:14.000 --> 04:14.640
Come here.

04:15.560 --> 04:16.360
Grab her.

04:17.480 --> 04:18.760
Mutou!

04:20.160 --> 04:21.079
Yuanbao, I'm fine.

04:21.079 --> 04:22.880
Let him go!

04:23.280 --> 04:24.880
Mutou!

04:28.120 --> 04:28.960
Mutou!

04:29.160 --> 04:30.000
Mutou!

04:31.600 --> 04:32.440
I'm fine.

04:33.320 --> 04:35.120
Stop hitting him!

04:35.560 --> 04:36.400
Mutou!

04:36.800 --> 04:37.960
Don't hit him!

04:38.000 --> 04:38.840
Mutou!

04:39.640 --> 04:40.520
Mutou!

04:41.080 --> 04:41.760
Run!

04:49.560 --> 04:50.560
Mutou!

04:51.120 --> 04:52.480
Mutou, how are you?

04:52.960 --> 04:54.440
Not a big deal.

04:58.760 --> 04:59.400
Mutou!

05:00.520 --> 05:01.360
Mutou!

05:02.440 --> 05:03.120
Mutou!

05:03.680 --> 05:04.360
Yuanbao,

05:05.400 --> 05:06.330
don't be afraid.

05:07.000 --> 05:08.130
I'm here to save you.

05:10.840 --> 05:11.840
Since then,

05:12.240 --> 05:14.160
even today, many years later,

05:14.480 --> 05:15.720
I can't recall

05:15.840 --> 05:17.840
the exact details of this incident.

05:18.040 --> 05:19.000
I only remember

05:19.560 --> 05:21.760
that Yuanbao cried for a very long time that day.

05:21.760 --> 05:24.320
When she cried, my heart ached.

05:24.960 --> 05:25.720
So,

05:26.320 --> 05:28.000
I can't let anyone bully her.

05:29.640 --> 05:31.320
Yuanbao, don't cry.

05:31.320 --> 05:33.520
When you cry, it makes me want to cry too.

05:44.120 --> 05:44.720
Mutou.

05:47.120 --> 05:47.840
Mutou.

05:50.080 --> 05:51.159
Don't hit him.

05:52.520 --> 05:53.600
Don't hit him.

05:55.400 --> 05:56.040
Yuanbao.

05:56.280 --> 05:57.560
Don't be afraid, child.

05:57.560 --> 05:58.960
Don't be afraid, I'm here.

05:58.960 --> 06:00.320
Everything is fine now.

06:00.520 --> 06:02.000
Auntie,

06:02.600 --> 06:05.120
I thought I'd never come back.

06:06.200 --> 06:07.280
You're back.

06:07.360 --> 06:09.420
Don't be afraid. Everything is fine.

06:09.920 --> 06:10.720
Mutou.

06:12.040 --> 06:12.770
How is Mutou?

06:12.960 --> 06:13.480
Mutou.

06:14.280 --> 06:16.480
Mutou is fine. His life is not in danger.

06:16.760 --> 06:18.120
He is in the next ward.

06:18.200 --> 06:20.000
Your uncle is taking care of him.

06:20.760 --> 06:22.040
Uncle is back too?

06:22.920 --> 06:24.360
As soon as he heard the news,

06:24.360 --> 06:26.400
he bought a flight ticket and came back immediately.

06:26.400 --> 06:28.040
Mr. Tian also just left.

06:28.440 --> 06:29.320
It's alright.

06:30.000 --> 06:30.880
You're back.

06:32.159 --> 06:34.000
Then how long have I been sleeping?

06:34.000 --> 06:36.400
You've been sleeping for two or three days.

06:37.159 --> 06:39.620
The doctor said you were overly frightened.

06:39.760 --> 06:42.080
But the injuries on your body are not a big problem.

06:42.080 --> 06:43.680
But you still need to rest well

06:43.680 --> 06:45.010
to recover your spirit.

06:46.320 --> 06:47.760
Then what about Grandma?

06:48.000 --> 06:49.600
Grandma hasn't recovered yet.

06:49.600 --> 06:50.560
Does Grandma know?

06:50.560 --> 06:52.240
Alright, don't worry.

06:52.760 --> 06:54.240
We didn't tell Grandma.

06:54.760 --> 06:56.320
We just told her

06:56.520 --> 06:59.360
you and Qingyun went to Shanghai for a competition.

06:59.360 --> 07:02.280
So don't show up in front of her these few days

07:02.440 --> 07:03.900
lest she gets suspicious.

07:05.480 --> 07:07.000
Then what about Mutou?

07:07.720 --> 07:10.000
Don't worry. Your uncle is there.

07:10.560 --> 07:12.280
Right, the police will come in a while

07:12.280 --> 07:13.680
to take your statement.

07:14.200 --> 07:15.000
Tell me,

07:15.040 --> 07:16.880
what exactly happened?

07:17.960 --> 07:18.840
The police?

07:18.960 --> 07:19.640
Yes.

07:19.800 --> 07:22.260
Those guys have been arrested by the police.

07:26.080 --> 07:26.760
Well?

07:27.280 --> 07:28.440
Have you made up your mind?

07:28.440 --> 07:29.120
Don't worry.

07:29.120 --> 07:31.480
I'll give you the other half of the money after the job is done.

07:31.480 --> 07:33.120
What kind of results do you want?

07:33.120 --> 07:36.520
Different results come at different prices.

07:37.320 --> 07:38.880
I don't want you to hit her.

07:39.120 --> 07:40.650
Just warn her and scare her.

07:41.040 --> 07:42.760
Just a little scare.

07:43.320 --> 07:45.840
What? You can't even do that?

07:45.880 --> 07:47.280
She's just a little girl.

07:47.280 --> 07:49.140
What's so hard about scaring her?

07:49.159 --> 07:51.920
Don't worry. Leave it to me.

07:52.400 --> 07:54.260
What do you have to say about this?

08:03.200 --> 08:04.000
Class.

08:04.720 --> 08:06.480
Recently, there has been a

08:06.560 --> 08:09.020
very serious vicious incident in our class.

08:09.480 --> 08:10.680
The school has issued an order

08:10.680 --> 08:12.080
for us to take this as a warning

08:12.080 --> 08:13.760
and prevent it from happening again.

08:13.760 --> 08:14.520
Therefore,

08:15.440 --> 08:17.240
the theme of our class meeting is

08:17.760 --> 08:19.720
preventing school bullying.

09:37.760 --> 09:39.840
Yuanbao, why are you here?

09:40.440 --> 09:42.500
Why didn't you rest well in your ward?

09:42.520 --> 09:43.440
I'm fine.

09:44.400 --> 09:45.080
Uncle,

09:46.760 --> 09:48.160
how is Mutou?

09:48.360 --> 09:51.760
The doctor said fortunately the wound on his head isn't deep,

09:51.840 --> 09:54.040
but his arm took a heavy blow

09:54.120 --> 09:55.040
and fractured.

09:58.360 --> 09:59.960
He'll need a long time to rest

10:00.000 --> 10:01.200
for it to heal slowly.

10:02.080 --> 10:04.680
I've already asked for leave for both of you at school.

10:04.680 --> 10:06.720
Just focus on recovering your health,

10:06.720 --> 10:08.780
and don't worry about anything else.

10:14.080 --> 10:15.200
It's all my fault.

10:15.760 --> 10:17.120
I shouldn't have gone abroad

10:17.120 --> 10:18.520
and been so far from home.

10:18.920 --> 10:21.040
I didn't take good care of you.

10:21.240 --> 10:22.080
Uncle,

10:22.680 --> 10:23.920
don't say that.

10:24.880 --> 10:27.000
How can you be blamed for this?

10:27.080 --> 10:28.340
Now that Uncle is back,

10:28.800 --> 10:29.680
I won't leave.

10:31.080 --> 10:32.940
I'll take good care of you at home.

10:34.320 --> 10:36.480
Money isn't important.

10:37.000 --> 10:38.000
What's important

10:38.480 --> 10:40.280
is that you are safe and healthy.

10:44.680 --> 10:45.320
Hello.

10:45.800 --> 10:46.600
I came to the hospital today

10:46.600 --> 10:48.460
specifically to see the two kids.

10:53.880 --> 10:55.560
This is a small token of my appreciation.

10:55.560 --> 10:56.600
Please accept it.

10:59.520 --> 11:01.240
It's just a little money for fruit.

11:01.240 --> 11:02.440
Please don't refuse.

11:02.840 --> 11:03.840
What do you mean?

11:04.240 --> 11:06.280
Do you think money makes you so great?

11:06.280 --> 11:08.360
Like mother, like daughter.

11:08.600 --> 11:09.720
With your filthy money,

11:09.720 --> 11:11.600
you can do whatever you want, right?

11:11.600 --> 11:13.640
I'm telling you, this isn't over.

11:13.800 --> 11:15.640
Your child is already 17 or 18 years old.

11:15.640 --> 11:17.320
After so many years of schooling,

11:17.320 --> 11:19.920
living in a family with such good material conditions,

11:19.920 --> 11:21.240
how do you educate her?

11:21.800 --> 11:24.280
Doesn't she even know the most basic principles of being a person?

11:24.280 --> 11:25.080
Yes.

11:25.480 --> 11:27.010
I've been too busy with work

11:27.160 --> 11:28.720
and neglected Xinrui's discipline.

11:28.720 --> 11:29.640
I never expected

11:29.640 --> 11:31.200
that after she reached puberty,

11:31.200 --> 11:32.600
she would be so rebellious

11:32.600 --> 11:34.060
and dare to do such a thing.

11:34.200 --> 11:35.120
Puberty?

11:35.560 --> 11:37.000
There are many kids in puberty.

11:37.000 --> 11:39.240
Our Yuanbao and Qingjun are both in puberty.

11:39.240 --> 11:40.280
Why didn't they do

11:40.360 --> 11:41.800
such illegal things?

11:42.120 --> 11:43.850
Don't use puberty as an excuse.

11:44.560 --> 11:46.080
What? Am I wrong?

11:49.440 --> 11:50.500
About this matter,

11:50.960 --> 11:53.160
I have already learned about it from the police.

11:53.160 --> 11:54.080
Our children

11:54.120 --> 11:55.840
really have no problems.

11:56.280 --> 11:57.000
As for your daughter,

11:57.000 --> 11:58.600
why she would do such a thing,

11:58.880 --> 12:01.120
I heard it's because Yuanbao last time

12:01.200 --> 12:03.720
beat her in the school cheerleading competition,

12:03.720 --> 12:06.160
and also because Yuanbao and Meng Jingu,

12:06.520 --> 12:07.480
that is,

12:07.800 --> 12:09.760
Yuanbao's desk mate, became closer,

12:09.760 --> 12:10.920
she felt uncomfortable,

12:10.920 --> 12:12.720
which led to this incident.

12:13.600 --> 12:14.800
We are all parents.

12:14.840 --> 12:16.160
We feel sorry for our children.

12:16.160 --> 12:17.960
We can all understand this.

12:18.520 --> 12:20.320
But feeling sorry for her is one thing.

12:20.320 --> 12:21.580
Education is another.

12:21.840 --> 12:23.080
The child has made a mistake now.

12:23.080 --> 12:25.240
If you don't let her take responsibility,

12:25.240 --> 12:27.600
it might not be a good thing for her.

12:30.360 --> 12:32.690
Our child suffered such severe injuries.

12:33.360 --> 12:35.360
Qingyun is still in a coma,

12:36.240 --> 12:38.770
and she might even have some lasting effects.

12:39.600 --> 12:40.560
As parents,

12:40.720 --> 12:42.080
we didn't take good care of our child,

12:42.080 --> 12:43.960
and we already blame ourselves enough.

12:43.960 --> 12:45.960
If we choose to settle for money,

12:46.320 --> 12:47.080
then we,

12:47.160 --> 12:48.890
we don't deserve to be parents.

12:51.120 --> 12:54.400
So, please don't mention the settlement again.

12:54.880 --> 12:57.320
Let's just follow the normal procedures, okay?

12:57.320 --> 12:59.080
The court and the police will judge

12:59.080 --> 13:00.740
according to their own rules.

13:01.480 --> 13:03.680
If you have time, you should think about

13:04.000 --> 13:04.800
how to properly

13:04.800 --> 13:06.720
educate your child in the future.

13:07.000 --> 13:08.860
I understand what you're saying.

13:09.440 --> 13:11.320
But Xinrui is only seventeen.

13:12.400 --> 13:13.480
If this happens,

13:14.480 --> 13:16.140
her whole life will be ruined.

13:16.760 --> 13:18.290
I know you don't lack money,

13:18.320 --> 13:21.180
but right now, money is the only way to make up for it.

13:21.560 --> 13:23.720
I can't do anything else.

13:24.360 --> 13:25.280
I beg you both,

13:25.480 --> 13:27.480
for the sake of me being a mother too,

13:28.200 --> 13:29.460
please understand me.

13:29.920 --> 13:31.920
Please give my daughter another chance.

13:31.920 --> 13:32.920
I understand you.

13:33.720 --> 13:35.520
Can you understand me?

13:36.160 --> 13:37.480
If the one lying on the hospital bed right now

13:37.480 --> 13:38.760
were your child?

13:39.000 --> 13:39.880
Let me tell you.

13:40.280 --> 13:41.880
The fact that I didn't treat your child

13:41.880 --> 13:44.680
the same way is already very understanding of you.

13:47.760 --> 13:50.560
Whose child isn't the apple of their mother's eye?

13:51.240 --> 13:52.240
If your child

13:53.440 --> 13:55.000
were beaten like this,

13:56.360 --> 13:57.420
how would you feel?

14:10.080 --> 14:11.410
Chairman, what's this?

14:15.360 --> 14:16.290
Are you alright?

14:19.560 --> 14:20.620
Don't be like this.

14:21.000 --> 14:22.200
I don't buy it.

14:57.480 --> 14:58.540
Bao, you're awake.

15:00.520 --> 15:02.400
I'll go home for a bit later

15:02.480 --> 15:04.520
to get some clothes for your uncle.

15:04.560 --> 15:06.560
He hasn't changed clothes for days.

15:07.840 --> 15:09.480
Be good and stay here.

15:10.200 --> 15:11.240
If anything happens,

15:11.240 --> 15:13.120
call me, okay?

15:13.760 --> 15:14.690
Have some water.

15:16.440 --> 15:17.360
Auntie.

15:18.080 --> 15:19.680
Thank you for your hard work.

15:22.480 --> 15:23.640
It's nothing.

15:24.280 --> 15:25.200
Both of you

15:25.720 --> 15:27.400
are our darlings.

15:28.680 --> 15:29.760
I'll be right back.

16:25.480 --> 16:26.360
Yuanbao,

16:27.280 --> 16:28.210
don't be afraid.

16:28.880 --> 16:30.010
I'm here to save you.

16:45.240 --> 16:45.840
Uncle.

16:46.240 --> 16:46.840
Uncle.

16:47.280 --> 16:48.280
Mutou is awake.

16:51.440 --> 16:52.300
My son is awake.

16:54.240 --> 16:55.100
My son is awake.

16:55.120 --> 16:55.760
Doctor,

16:56.520 --> 16:57.560
my son is awake.

16:58.240 --> 17:01.200
Mutou, I was worried to death.

17:01.560 --> 17:02.840
It hurts.

17:04.040 --> 17:05.359
You have a fracture.

17:05.400 --> 17:07.460
The doctor said you need to rest well.

17:08.000 --> 17:11.000
Yuanbao, I'm fine.

17:11.400 --> 17:12.760
I'm tough.

17:13.839 --> 17:15.560
I'll be better in a while.

17:26.920 --> 17:28.319
You want to change seats.

17:29.920 --> 17:32.050
I want to switch seats with Mu Qingjun.

17:33.400 --> 17:34.040
Okay.

17:34.560 --> 17:36.620
Tell me if you need anything anytime.

17:37.560 --> 17:39.440
Thank you, Ms. Tian. I will.

17:39.960 --> 17:42.400
I'll go back and switch seats now.

17:50.360 --> 17:51.240
Xinrui's mom.

17:52.080 --> 17:53.000
Jingu's mom and I

17:53.000 --> 17:54.480
just heard about this.

17:56.000 --> 17:58.520
I didn't expect Xinrui to be so impulsive.

17:58.840 --> 18:01.080
It's my fault for being too busy with work

18:01.080 --> 18:03.010
and neglecting to discipline her.

18:03.240 --> 18:05.600
Don't blame yourself. It's our fault.

18:06.400 --> 18:07.480
Since Xinrui came back,

18:07.480 --> 18:08.920
we should have let her stay here.

18:08.920 --> 18:10.480
We didn't do our best.

18:10.760 --> 18:12.020
Please don't say that.

18:12.840 --> 18:13.960
You care about her

18:14.360 --> 18:16.160
even more than I do as her mother.

18:16.760 --> 18:19.600
I've always been very grateful to you.

18:20.160 --> 18:21.120
Not at all.

18:21.800 --> 18:23.200
Actually, I'm here today

18:24.360 --> 18:27.680
to ask Jingu for a favor.

18:30.080 --> 18:31.280
What are you talking about?

18:31.280 --> 18:33.410
He's just a kid. There's no need to ask.

18:33.440 --> 18:35.120
Just tell us what you need.

18:35.760 --> 18:36.680
It's like this.

18:37.720 --> 18:38.640
Today,

18:38.800 --> 18:40.730
I went to see the victims' parents.

18:41.040 --> 18:42.960
I intended to settle it financially

18:42.960 --> 18:45.040
and then transfer Xinrui to another school.

18:45.040 --> 18:46.800
But they were too stubborn.

18:47.000 --> 18:48.860
I said all the good things I could,

18:49.640 --> 18:51.840
but they just wouldn't agree to settle.

18:53.400 --> 18:54.120
Of course,

18:54.720 --> 18:56.450
I can understand how they feel.

18:56.800 --> 18:57.640
But,

19:00.960 --> 19:02.760
Xinrui is only seventeen.

19:03.200 --> 19:05.080
If we really go through the legal process,

19:05.080 --> 19:07.540
she'll carry a stain for the rest of her life.

19:08.040 --> 19:08.800
Jingu,

19:09.360 --> 19:11.090
you and Xinrui grew up together

19:11.480 --> 19:12.840
like siblings.

19:13.080 --> 19:14.740
Even if Xinrui made a mistake,

19:15.520 --> 19:18.320
she should be given a chance to turn over a new leaf.

19:20.120 --> 19:20.880
Jingu,

19:21.400 --> 19:22.600
Aunt Gu is talking to you.

19:22.600 --> 19:24.060
Why are you keeping quiet?

19:24.200 --> 19:25.000
I heard

19:26.480 --> 19:28.740
when Mu Qingjun was sent to the hospital,

19:29.560 --> 19:31.960
his head was covered in blood. Is that true?

19:32.320 --> 19:33.640
If he's too seriously injured

19:33.640 --> 19:35.080
and left with sequelae,

19:35.640 --> 19:37.840
what's the point of giving him more money?

19:37.840 --> 19:39.480
His life might be ruined.

19:40.160 --> 19:41.120
Do you know

19:43.920 --> 19:45.520
he actually has good grades.

19:49.600 --> 19:50.840
I know what you mean.

19:51.920 --> 19:52.980
But think about it,

19:53.880 --> 19:56.200
it's not like Xinrui asked those people to beat them.

19:56.200 --> 19:58.060
She didn't expect this to happen.

19:58.320 --> 19:59.920
She didn't expect those kids

20:00.160 --> 20:01.760
to actually start fighting.

20:03.200 --> 20:04.400
It is indeed too much.

20:07.200 --> 20:08.040
I know.

20:08.680 --> 20:09.740
Saying all this now

20:09.760 --> 20:10.840
is meaningless.

20:12.160 --> 20:15.020
But even if Xinrui bears the legal responsibility,

20:15.440 --> 20:16.320
those two kids won't

20:16.320 --> 20:18.120
get better immediately, right?

20:18.200 --> 20:20.460
It's better to accept this compensation

20:20.840 --> 20:23.680
as a guarantee for their future.

20:24.760 --> 20:26.760
What's the point of telling me this?

20:26.960 --> 20:27.600
Jingu,

20:27.880 --> 20:29.960
how could you talk to Aunt Gu like that?

20:29.960 --> 20:30.720
Exactly.

20:31.000 --> 20:32.260
You are unbelievable.

20:32.720 --> 20:33.600
Jingu,

20:33.880 --> 20:35.340
can you go to the hospital?

20:35.560 --> 20:37.800
Talk to that kid named Xiong Yuanbao

20:38.000 --> 20:39.760
and get them to agree to a settlement.

20:39.760 --> 20:41.920
I know you can't let go of your pride.

20:42.040 --> 20:42.840
But...

20:44.400 --> 20:45.320
I beg you.

20:45.360 --> 20:46.840
Please save our Xinrui.

20:47.680 --> 20:48.720
Jingu.

20:48.720 --> 20:51.120
You have to understand Aunt Gu's feelings.

20:51.560 --> 20:52.360
It seems

20:53.680 --> 20:55.800
I have to ask for this favor, right?

20:56.200 --> 20:57.080
Jingu,

20:57.680 --> 20:58.400
you see,

20:58.800 --> 21:00.680
you and that Xiong Yuanbao

21:00.800 --> 21:01.800
are desk mates.

21:02.200 --> 21:03.680
You have a good relationship too.

21:03.680 --> 21:05.560
It's easier to communicate

21:05.880 --> 21:07.160
when people of the same age talk to each other.

21:07.160 --> 21:08.080
Besides,

21:08.440 --> 21:09.920
you wouldn't just watch

21:09.960 --> 21:11.360
Xinrui get into trouble.

21:11.600 --> 21:12.480
Jingu,

21:13.000 --> 21:14.560
go and talk to Xiong Yuanbao.

21:14.560 --> 21:16.200
As long as she agrees to settle,

21:16.200 --> 21:18.460
no matter what conditions she proposes,

21:18.920 --> 21:20.050
I will agree to them.

21:21.680 --> 21:23.000
If their condition is

21:23.240 --> 21:24.840
to beat Xinrui the same way,

21:25.040 --> 21:26.240
would you agree too?

21:27.600 --> 21:28.160
You!

21:29.200 --> 21:30.120
You brat!

21:30.280 --> 21:31.400
What nonsense are you talking about?

21:31.400 --> 21:32.260
Come back here!

21:32.600 --> 21:33.520
Alright.

21:34.600 --> 21:35.320
Sit down.

21:48.000 --> 21:51.040
How could Xinrui do such a thing?

21:51.960 --> 21:53.640
She used to be such a good kid.

21:54.080 --> 21:56.200
I know you're sad,

21:56.880 --> 21:57.560
but...

21:57.640 --> 21:58.360
Mom.

21:58.960 --> 22:01.440
Okay, I'll stop talking.

22:08.000 --> 22:10.080
We'll buy this.

22:11.120 --> 22:11.920
You know,

22:12.000 --> 22:14.560
your father was firmly against it at first.

22:15.080 --> 22:16.540
He's willing to buy it now,

22:17.240 --> 22:18.760
and I think you know why.

22:19.480 --> 22:20.680
Whether you go or not,

22:20.960 --> 22:22.690
whether you help Xinrui or not,

22:23.120 --> 22:24.160
it's up to you.

22:27.360 --> 22:29.090
Son, think about it carefully.

22:59.200 --> 22:59.960
Hello,

23:00.040 --> 23:01.120
Auntie.

23:01.240 --> 23:02.400
Hello.

23:02.680 --> 23:03.320
Qiao Yan,

23:03.640 --> 23:04.240
Monitor,

23:04.640 --> 23:05.640
you are all here.

23:06.520 --> 23:07.280
Then you guys...

23:07.280 --> 23:09.410
I'll go out and buy you some breakfast.

23:09.560 --> 23:10.360
Goodbye,

23:10.360 --> 23:11.000
Auntie.

23:11.040 --> 23:11.680
Bye.

23:15.040 --> 23:16.900
The kiwis I bought are very sweet.

23:19.240 --> 23:21.120
Mr. Tian said you two are much better,

23:21.120 --> 23:23.560
so we can send representatives to visit you.

23:23.560 --> 23:25.440
We couldn't wait to come over.

23:27.480 --> 23:28.960
You have no idea.

23:29.120 --> 23:32.360
We were worried sick during this time.

23:32.440 --> 23:33.840
Yeah, worried sick.

23:33.920 --> 23:35.920
By the way, Mutou woke up last night.

23:36.280 --> 23:38.560
Let's quietly go and give him a surprise, okay?

23:38.560 --> 23:39.160
Okay.

23:39.160 --> 23:40.680
Then I'll bring some flowers for Qingyun.

23:40.680 --> 23:41.240
Let's go.

23:41.320 --> 23:42.080
Are you okay?

23:42.200 --> 23:43.080
I'm fine.

23:44.240 --> 23:45.200
Slow down, Yuanbao.

23:45.200 --> 23:46.330
I'm perfectly fine.

23:54.400 --> 23:55.660
Yuanbao, you're here.

23:56.080 --> 23:57.340
To give you a surprise.

23:57.760 --> 23:58.680
Surprise!

23:58.720 --> 24:01.160
Brother Qingyun, we are here.

24:01.240 --> 24:01.720
Surprise!

24:01.720 --> 24:03.520
How is it? Are you surprised?

24:03.560 --> 24:04.600
Are you excited?

24:04.640 --> 24:06.240
Did you miss us?

24:06.880 --> 24:08.640
Guys, you're all here.

24:08.840 --> 24:10.200
Bought you some fruits.

24:10.280 --> 24:12.000
I put them all in Yuanbao's room.

24:12.000 --> 24:13.730
Wishing you a speedy recovery.

24:14.240 --> 24:14.920
Qingyun,

24:14.960 --> 24:16.680
I hope you bounce back soon.

24:17.440 --> 24:19.500
Qingyun, wish you a speedy recovery.

24:20.800 --> 24:23.330
May you eat all you want and never gain weight.

24:24.840 --> 24:26.000
I'm fine.

24:26.600 --> 24:28.680
I just can't pick my nose.

24:29.240 --> 24:30.720
Stop moving.

24:31.000 --> 24:31.800
Thank you all.

24:32.600 --> 24:33.720
I'm fine now.

24:34.000 --> 24:35.960
But Mutou is seriously injured.

24:36.440 --> 24:38.080
He can't move his hands.

24:38.440 --> 24:39.520
But the doctor said

24:39.640 --> 24:40.800
as long as he rests well,

24:40.800 --> 24:42.000
he will recover soon.

24:42.600 --> 24:43.880
How is it, Qingyun?

24:44.200 --> 24:45.760
You're the top guy at Zhicheng.

24:45.760 --> 24:47.080
Our lineup today

24:48.240 --> 24:49.500
is pretty good, right?

24:49.640 --> 24:52.080
Thank you, everyone. Thank you.

24:53.320 --> 24:55.320
Don't move. You can talk to them.

24:55.840 --> 24:58.080
By the way, let me tell you some news.

24:58.920 --> 25:01.440
Yesterday, wasn't I called to Mr. Men's office

25:01.440 --> 25:03.520
for a heart-to-heart talk?

25:03.960 --> 25:06.880
I heard Mr. Men talking with other teachers.

25:07.080 --> 25:08.160
Guess what they were talking about.

25:08.160 --> 25:11.280
Were they saying you don't need to go to college,

25:11.440 --> 25:14.040
and just inherit your father's fortune-telling stall?

25:14.040 --> 25:15.200
Nice one, Yuanbao.

25:15.560 --> 25:17.890
Yuanbao, has your head not recovered yet?

25:18.840 --> 25:19.800
Mr. Men said

25:19.880 --> 25:22.240
before the end of this semester,

25:22.480 --> 25:24.920
he plans to take us on a field trip.

25:26.320 --> 25:27.080
Really?

25:28.160 --> 25:29.920
Then we can all go have fun together.

25:29.920 --> 25:30.680
Yes.

25:33.440 --> 25:34.560
Can I go too?

25:38.560 --> 25:39.520
Hero Gong Yu.

25:39.560 --> 25:40.640
Hero.

25:41.080 --> 25:42.240
Are you staying in this hospital too?

25:42.240 --> 25:43.680
I heard Mu Qingjun is awake.

25:43.680 --> 25:45.280
Can I move in to stay with you?

25:46.600 --> 25:47.320
No problem.

25:47.600 --> 25:49.400
There's an empty bed right here.

25:49.760 --> 25:50.440
Whatever.

25:50.800 --> 25:51.760
Come, let me help you.

25:51.760 --> 25:52.520
Let me help.

25:52.640 --> 25:53.320
Careful, careful.

25:53.320 --> 25:53.920
Slow down.

25:54.120 --> 25:55.160
Slow down, hero.

25:56.040 --> 25:57.080
Come, slow down.

25:58.000 --> 25:59.660
Your injury is quite serious.

25:59.720 --> 26:00.320
Slow down, slow down.

26:00.320 --> 26:01.000
Hurry.

26:01.320 --> 26:02.850
Slow down, slow down. Come.

26:03.240 --> 26:04.480
You must be Yuanbao.

26:06.320 --> 26:07.000
Yes.

26:07.160 --> 26:08.560
Okay, okay, that's fine.

26:08.760 --> 26:10.160
You classmates chat.

26:10.400 --> 26:12.800
I'll go pack some things for Xiaoyu.

26:13.360 --> 26:13.880
Okay, okay.

26:13.880 --> 26:14.680
You guys chat.

26:14.880 --> 26:15.600
Bye, Grandpa.

26:15.600 --> 26:16.240
Goodbye, Grandpa.

26:16.240 --> 26:17.240
Goodbye, goodbye.

26:17.240 --> 26:18.360
Not bad.

26:18.480 --> 26:20.840
The two heroes are sharing a room.

26:21.480 --> 26:22.760
It's gonna be lively.

26:24.160 --> 26:25.600
Well, when we go on the outing together,

26:25.600 --> 26:27.600
I plan to wear my most handsome clothes,

26:27.600 --> 26:30.960
and then give you guys a Chris Lee concert.

26:31.240 --> 26:34.320
I only have you in my heart, not him.

26:34.360 --> 26:37.120
You must believe my affection is not fake.

26:37.440 --> 26:38.240
Shang Ningyu,

26:38.280 --> 26:39.280
I think you can

26:39.320 --> 26:40.720
add another bed here.

26:44.000 --> 26:47.460
Your singing makes me feel like my condition is getting worse.

26:48.920 --> 26:50.580
You girls don't laugh either.

26:50.760 --> 26:52.160
Can you guys dress up a bit?

26:52.160 --> 26:53.920
Don't act like a dude all day.

26:54.000 --> 26:54.800
Shang Ningyu,

26:55.360 --> 26:56.720
watch your words.

26:56.880 --> 26:58.200
Be careful,

26:58.760 --> 27:00.160
or Yuanbao will bite you.

27:02.800 --> 27:03.480
Well.

27:03.720 --> 27:05.120
Let's take a group photo,

27:05.120 --> 27:06.640
since everyone is fine.

27:07.440 --> 27:07.770
Sure.

27:07.800 --> 27:08.560
Sure, sure.

27:08.600 --> 27:09.040
Sure.

27:09.080 --> 27:10.120
Come on, let's take a photo.

27:10.120 --> 27:12.720
Your brother looks like a mess and you still want a photo?

27:12.720 --> 27:14.000
Come on, bro, let's take one.

27:14.000 --> 27:16.440
I'll count 3, 2, 1, and everyone say cheese.

27:19.600 --> 27:21.360
Cheese.

27:24.200 --> 27:25.120
Take one more.

27:25.120 --> 27:26.450
Let me tell you, Gong Yu.

27:37.520 --> 27:38.400
What's wrong?

27:40.400 --> 27:40.960
Well,

27:41.120 --> 27:41.840
bros,

27:41.880 --> 27:43.760
we'll visit you again when we're free.

27:43.760 --> 27:46.360
We'll head out first.

27:46.480 --> 27:46.800
Yeah,

27:46.800 --> 27:47.860
we're heading out.

27:48.160 --> 27:49.120
Bye, Qingyun.

27:49.280 --> 27:49.960
Let's go.

27:51.120 --> 27:51.800
Let's go.

27:59.680 --> 28:00.400
Bye.

28:21.960 --> 28:23.320
How are you feeling?

28:24.520 --> 28:25.320
Much better.

28:27.040 --> 28:28.900
I didn't know what you like to eat,

28:29.040 --> 28:30.360
so I just bought whatever.

28:30.360 --> 28:31.120
Thank you.

28:31.320 --> 28:32.850
You really shouldn't have.

28:33.080 --> 28:35.320
Qingyun, about this time,

28:36.240 --> 28:37.520
I am really sorry.

28:38.280 --> 28:39.410
It's not your fault.

28:39.440 --> 28:40.900
Let's go outside and talk.

28:41.280 --> 28:42.940
Let's not disturb their rest.

29:10.280 --> 29:11.320
I am really sorry.

29:15.120 --> 29:17.320
Actually, you don't have to apologize.

29:17.920 --> 29:18.480
I...

29:20.640 --> 29:22.570
I'm sorry for what happened to you.

29:24.040 --> 29:25.300
Don't blame yourself.

29:28.360 --> 29:29.440
This time,

29:30.120 --> 29:31.040
I am not just

29:35.240 --> 29:36.760
apologizing for myself.

29:39.680 --> 29:41.880
You're here to apologize for Gu Xinrui.

29:47.560 --> 29:49.890
If you are here to apologize for Gu Xinrui,

29:50.720 --> 29:52.580
then it's even more unnecessary.

29:52.640 --> 29:54.970
You weren't the one who sent those people.

29:55.280 --> 29:57.120
The culprit hasn't even apologized,

29:57.120 --> 29:58.480
so why should you?

30:00.520 --> 30:01.320
Go back.

30:01.560 --> 30:02.640
Class is about to start.

30:02.640 --> 30:03.320
Yuanbao,

30:04.200 --> 30:04.920
I know

30:05.880 --> 30:07.360
this is too much to ask,

30:08.760 --> 30:10.690
but her family has been begging me.

30:11.560 --> 30:13.360
Can you give her another chance?

30:13.440 --> 30:15.080
If you take legal action,

30:15.360 --> 30:17.040
her life might be ruined.

30:18.360 --> 30:19.200
Meng Jingu,

30:19.720 --> 30:20.920
if you came here today

30:21.120 --> 30:22.840
with a sincere apology,

30:24.320 --> 30:25.600
I appreciate it.

30:28.080 --> 30:29.200
But if you came today

30:29.200 --> 30:30.560
to plead for Gu Xinrui,

30:31.280 --> 30:32.280
you should leave.

30:32.360 --> 30:33.690
I'm not that forgiving.

30:33.960 --> 30:34.640
Yuanbao,

30:35.760 --> 30:36.480
I'm sorry.

30:37.960 --> 30:39.160
I know you're angry,

30:39.440 --> 30:40.640
but I have my reasons.

30:40.960 --> 30:42.040
Can you tell me

30:43.360 --> 30:44.520
what they can do

30:46.440 --> 30:47.640
to make it up to you?

30:50.080 --> 30:51.000
Angry?

30:53.320 --> 30:54.920
Is it just about being angry?

30:55.080 --> 30:56.400
Do you know what

30:56.520 --> 30:57.920
we went through that day?

30:58.880 --> 31:00.440
Do you know

31:02.040 --> 31:03.640
how fragile human bones are?

31:04.320 --> 31:05.520
One hit with a stick

31:07.320 --> 31:08.840
can break them.

31:11.240 --> 31:12.520
Do you know that the blood

31:12.520 --> 31:13.780
flowing out of the body

31:13.800 --> 31:14.800
is hot

31:16.040 --> 31:17.080
and sticky?

31:18.640 --> 31:20.600
Do you know what despair is?

31:21.160 --> 31:24.120
You said Gu Xinrui's life would be ruined.

31:26.040 --> 31:27.040
When she gets out,

31:27.520 --> 31:29.050
she can just go back to the UK

31:29.080 --> 31:31.040
and continue being a rich girl.

31:31.560 --> 31:32.760
But what about Mutou?

31:34.680 --> 31:36.000
You saw him just now.

31:36.720 --> 31:39.000
What if he suffers from lingering effects?

31:39.000 --> 31:41.080
What if he gets disabled?

31:43.080 --> 31:44.800
Who exactly harmed whom?

31:45.720 --> 31:46.840
Tell me!
